name: sacrifice and reward part 1
description:
Animated oil painting in mp4 video to run in loop 

"I understood what I had to do, so I sacrificed my time along with my focus, my mobility, my mind, my dedication... It wasn't enough, I had to sacrifice my paradigms, my habits, my reality... It's always time to find yourself innocent and abandon your newly understood innocence right away. "
